The attached script will change dial permissions on a netsapiens SNAPsolution softswitch based on voipmonitor reaching a billing limit. See https://www.voipmonitor.org/doc/Billing for more info.

1) Load the script to your QoS server

2) Make the script executable 
chmod +x billinglimit.php

3) In your Alert with type Watchdog: billing over quota
Ensure summary is NOT checked
In the external script field enter the path to your script and filename e.g. /home/ubuntu/billinglimit.php

